I’m so excited to share with you my recent scalp and hair treatment. I have spend a lot of time at home during my pregnancy but because of these products I was able to bring that fresh-from-the-salon feeling at home.

This perfect duo leaves the hair strengthened,clean and hydrated.
I organised a discount for you guys so make sure to use it when you check out! Discount code: SARAHANGIUS
